title: Magnificent Film
review: This movie is so breathtaking; taking into account it's special effects and overall acting. Definitely recommend watching this movie to anyone who likes a movie with lots of surprise thrills.

movie_title: Star Wars: Episode VIII - The Last Jedi
title: An Alright Movie
review: The Last Jedi is to some people considered to be a great movie, though it has a great plot; it lacks certain components of a what would be a fantastic movie.
